	   <tr><td colspan=2>well, right now i'm lvl 7 and stuff and i was wondering where would be the best place to attack monsters. I really like being a mage too, I think I couldn't have chosen better.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
