<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=99527191283218></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f99527191283218><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=12&mid=99527191283218>RE: aaladieni</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=12&mid=99527191283218#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=20521><span id= >Kelendin</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>16 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Mon, Jul 16th 4:25 AM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Well, ofcourse it depends in what area are you? If youre Feydwer, Id say CB or Steamfont. Well, yeah, CB is a hell on earth, but Steamfont is fine. Watch out for trains in CB. And dont pull too far, or youll pull the whole crushbone with you. Well, steamfont, I dont really know, skels and minos, mino axes selling around 10pp. I dont know much about Steamfont.<br><br>If youre in Antonica, Id say EC. You can hunt bears and wolves, and when you hit 8, maybe join an orcgroup. Only buy water pet first. Why? Well becouse its an allrounder and earth and air are almost useless. And you get damageshield too (shield of fire) so you dont have to use fire to get it. You can get the other pets later, when you have more money to play with. That shock of blades does 31dmg, so its an obvius increse to your burn. Remember to collect all DeathFist belts, Hazran in Freeport Militia will give you insane exp. (8 of them, 1 orange bar at 10) and DF belts sometimes sell for 2pp, so its a nice profit. If you go solo, then hunt darkweed snakes and be sure to choose water pet. Its almost immune to poison. <br><br>Then at 10 - 12 hunt wisps, becouse youre going to need the extra cash to buy level 12 spells. Lightstones sell for 7gp to vendors and greater lighstones 10pp to players. You can also do the quest in Karana to get 9pp and faction. I think theres all?<br><br>~Zerlax<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
